stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> RESERVED: Redis Lua 预占成功

    RESERVED --> PUBLISHED: MQ 发送已确认
    RESERVED --> RECONCILING: 发送超时/进程宕机/扫描发现超龄

    PUBLISHED --> PROCESSING: 消费开始
    PROCESSING --> ORDERED: PostgreSQL 事务提交

    PUBLISHED --> RECONCILING: 消息长期无结果
    PROCESSING --> RECONCILING: 数据库提交结果未知

    RECONCILING --> PUBLISHED: 确认消息存在或补发成功
    RECONCILING --> ORDERED: 查到有效订单
    RECONCILING --> RELEASE_PENDING: 确认无订单且不会再创建

    RESERVED --> RELEASE_PENDING: 明确发送失败且安全释放
    PROCESSING --> RELEASE_PENDING: PostgreSQL 确定性业务失败

    RELEASE_PENDING --> RELEASED: 补偿 CAS 成功

    RECONCILING --> MANUAL_REVIEW: 超出自动修复预算
